name_for_human: Generate Image Condition On Line Image
description_for_human: useful when you want to generate a new real image from both the user description and a straight line image.
description_for_model: useful when you want to generate a new real image from both the user description and a straight line image. like: generate a real image of a object or something from this straight line image, or generate a new real image of a object or something from this straight lines. The input to this tool should be the image_path and the user description.
